</div>
<span id="ライフハッカーになる"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AB.E3.83.BC.E3.81.AB.E3.81.AA.E3.82.8B"><div class="method_label">方法 1 の 10:</div>ライフハッカーになる</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_1" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-00">
<a name="step_1_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 1というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a8df98909fe2020c3a28795a23d83ed2" onload="WH.performance.clearMarks('image1_rendered'); WH.performance.mark('image1_rendered');" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('a8df98909fe2020c3a28795a23d83ed2')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 1というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-1.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a8df98909fe2020c3a28795a23d83ed2" onload="WH.performance.clearMarks('image1_rendered'); WH.performance.mark('image1_rendered');"></noscript>
