<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 2というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/0b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/0b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dae694d15a560698fd8e2bf04b791b6b"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/0b\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/0b\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ライフハックを探す　</b><a href="/%E3%83%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%83%9A%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B8" title="メインページ">ウィキハウ</a>で様々なライフハックを検索し、より詳しい方法を探しましょう。ウィキハウには様々なライフハックが満載です。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-02">
<a name="step_1_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 3というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d00fe4b87bfaa55a5cb2bd2da586ea0c" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('d00fe4b87bfaa55a5cb2bd2da586ea0c')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 3というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d00fe4b87bfaa55a5cb2bd2da586ea0c"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/c7\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/c7\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">YouTubeで「ライフハック」を検索し、ここで取り上げるもの以外のものも探してみる　</b>人々が実際に発見・実践しているライフハックを見ることができます。
