<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>2</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="キッチンのライフハック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.82.AD.E3.83.83.E3.83.81.E3.83.B3.E3.81.AE.E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 2 の 10:</div>キッチンのライフハック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_2" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-13">
<a name="step_2_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 4というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c3/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="37b163f1a5bee5a5452c15b3d5207b68" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c3/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('37b163f1a5bee5a5452c15b3d5207b68')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 4というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/c3/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c3/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="37b163f1a5bee5a5452c15b3d5207b68"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/c3\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/c3\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">沸騰している鍋の上に木製のスプーンを乗せ、吹きこぼれを防ぐ　</b>沸騰した水によって作られる泡の中は蒸気でいっぱいです。そのため、泡が100°C以下の物体に触れると蒸気は液化（液体に戻ること）し、泡の表面がはじけます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-14">
<a name="step_2_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 5というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="92f97893dbc0f8fd17aad0982dee28c2" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('92f97893dbc0f8fd17aad0982dee28c2')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 5というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="92f97893dbc0f8fd17aad0982dee28c2"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/d\/d5\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/d\/d5\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ズボン用のハンガーを安価なレシピホルダーとして使う　</b>究極のディナーを作ろうとしたものの、レシピ本を見るためにキッチンを何度もうろうろして料理を焦がしてしまった、という人は多いでしょう。これを避けるために、レシピ本をズボンハンガーに挟み、食器棚の取っ手などに引っ掛けて使います。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-15">
<a name="step_2_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 6というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bf/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="3c45d4cda0c8f5078ebe124df899d1c1" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/bf/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('3c45d4cda0c8f5078ebe124df899d1c1')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 6というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/bf/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bf/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="3c45d4cda0c8f5078ebe124df899d1c1"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/bf\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/bf\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-6.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">濡れたキッチンペーパーで飲み物のボトルをくるみ、冷凍庫に入れる　</b>冷凍庫内に水が滴り落ちないように、キッチンペーパーを軽く絞ります。ボトルを15分も冷凍庫に入れておけばしっかりと冷えることでしょう。これはボトルを冷やしたい場合や、冷凍庫に氷がない場合に役立ちます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-16">
<a name="step_2_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 7というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="20866c39d3520f0d7eb2036a705896fe" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('20866c39d3520f0d7eb2036a705896fe')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 7というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="20866c39d3520f0d7eb2036a705896fe"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/e0\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/e0\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-7.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">パンケーキの生地をケチャップの容器に入れる　</b>こうすれば生地をきちんと保存でき、カウンターに生地が垂れてべたべたになることもなく、ボウルにラップをかけて保存するという面倒な手間も必要ありません。じょうごを使ってケチャップボトルの開口部から生地を流し込みます。さらにライフハックをもう一つ。じょうごもボトルで作れます！
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-17">
<a name="step_2_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 8というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="56927b66a8e953cf46547b49dc4b6ebd" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('56927b66a8e953cf46547b49dc4b6ebd')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 8というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="56927b66a8e953cf46547b49dc4b6ebd"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/3\/3a\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/3\/3a\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-8.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">バーベキューの際にマフィン型を調味料入れに使う　</b>マフィン型に一つ一つ調味料を入れておけば、調味料が混ざり合って不気味な味のソースになることもありません。また、後片付けも簡単です。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-18">
<a name="step_2_6" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 9というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7d/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="ea856bfaad985792581c74b7a25be166" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/7d/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('ea856bfaad985792581c74b7a25be166')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 9というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/7d/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7d/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="ea856bfaad985792581c74b7a25be166"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/7d\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/7d\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-9.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">6</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ストローで<a href="/%E3%82%A4%E3%83%81%E3%82%B4%E3%82%92%E8%82%B2%E3%81%A6%E3%82%8B" title="イチゴを育てる"><b class="whb">イチゴ</b></a>のへたを取る　</b>この方法は簡単で効果的なだけでなく、へたを切り落とすと無駄になる部分を傷つけずに残すことができます。いちごの下部からストローを差し込み、へたが飛び出すまで押し込みます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-19">
<a name="step_2_7" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 10というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6e/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0b4f1f9009b1cac9214a1c2cfbda162a" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/6e/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('0b4f1f9009b1cac9214a1c2cfbda162a')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 10というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/6e/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6e/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="0b4f1f9009b1cac9214a1c2cfbda162a"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/6\/6e\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/6\/6e\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-10.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">7</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">レモンを絞る時、トングを使ってしっかり絞る　</b>半分に切ったレモンをトングの間に挟みます。通常ものを挟む先端の部分を持って絞ります。こうするとレモン汁を無駄なく絞り切ることができます。使用後はきれいに洗いましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-110">
<a name="step_2_8" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 11というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/1c/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="f0987d636e8468ef5a8eb8c25390f520" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/1c/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('f0987d636e8468ef5a8eb8c25390f520')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 11というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/1c/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/1c/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="f0987d636e8468ef5a8eb8c25390f520"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/1\/1c\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/1\/1c\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-11.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">8</div><div class="step">
<a href="/%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AD%E3%82%92%E4%BD%9C%E3%82%8B" title="ケーキを作る"><b class="whb">ケーキ</b></a><b class="whb">、チーズ、シナモンロール、フォンダンなどの柔らかいものを切る時は、糸巻型のデンタルフロスを使う　</b>こういった食品は、柔軟で細い糸で切ることができます。糸状のデンタルフロスを両手で持ち、しっかりと引っ張ります。粘土を切る時に針金を使うのと同じ要領です。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-111">
<a name="step_2_9" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-12.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 12というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/df/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-12.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-12.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fe111f0358b87424502a2c734f4fcdee" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/df/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-12.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-12.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('fe111f0358b87424502a2c734f4fcdee')</script>
