<div class="step_num">12</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">プラスチックの蓋をコースターとして使う　</b>手元にコースターがない場合、よくあるプラスチック容器の蓋が使えます。グラスを乗せるだけで、きちんとしたコースターとして使えます。よく洗ってから使用しましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-115">
<a name="step_2_13" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 16というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/72/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a566ff1d3404e0f1e16ea175658409f8" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/72/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('a566ff1d3404e0f1e16ea175658409f8')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 16というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/72/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/72/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="a566ff1d3404e0f1e16ea175658409f8"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/72\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/72\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-16.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">13</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">残り物のピザはフライパンやスキレットで温める　</b>こうすることで、ピザ生地が柔らかくなり、乾燥してしまうのを防ぎます。お好みで、少量の油を加えても良いでしょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-116">
<a name="step_2_14" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 17というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="11f62631cbc7a7766752301ca9aaccb8" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('11f62631cbc7a7766752301ca9aaccb8')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 17というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e6/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="11f62631cbc7a7766752301ca9aaccb8"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/e6\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/e6\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-17.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">14</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">牛乳をシリアルに注ぐ時、スプーンを裏返しにしてボウルに置く　</b>こうすると、牛乳が周囲に飛び散ってベタベタになるのを防ぎます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-117">
<a name="step_2_15" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 18というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/08/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="bb08aaa2d3d357adee3aa9b34f91f5c6" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/08/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('bb08aaa2d3d357adee3aa9b34f91f5c6')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 18というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/08/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/08/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="bb08aaa2d3d357adee3aa9b34f91f5c6"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/08\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/08\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-18.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">15</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">卵の白身と黄身を分ける時にペットボトルを使う　</b><a href="/%E5%8D%B5%E3%82%92%E5%89%B2%E3%82%8B" title="卵を割る">卵を割り</a>、ボトルを少し絞ります。飲み口を黄身に近づけると、黄身が突然吸い込まれます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="wh_ad_inner w_label al_grey" data-service="adsense" data-slot="6771527778" data-width="728" data-height="90" data-smallheight="250" data-type="method" data-small="1" data-medium="1" data-channels="8866763126" data-mobilechannels="" data-largechannels="" data-smallchannels="" data-observerloading="1" data-sizes-array="0" data-gptdisplaylate="1"><div id="mobilemethod_ad_2"></div></div>
