<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
</ol>
<div class="clearall"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>3</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="寝室・浴室のライフハック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.AF.9D.E5.AE.A4.E3.83.BB.E6.B5.B4.E5.AE.A4.E3.81.AE.E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 3 の 10:</div>寝室・浴室のライフハック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_3" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-218">
<a name="step_3_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 19というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e7c4d4be0f340f6b9d6140c6e94c5283" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/a8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('e7c4d4be0f340f6b9d6140c6e94c5283')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 19というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/a8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e7c4d4be0f340f6b9d6140c6e94c5283"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/a\/a8\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/a8\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-19.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">雑誌や書類用の収納ケースをキャビネットのドアの内側に取り付け、ヘアドライヤーを収納する　</b>雑誌や書類の収納ケースはドライヤーにぴったりのサイズで、ねじ止めすると安定します。ねじ止めができない場合は、しっかりとくっつくコマンドタブや両面テープ、裏面にテープがついたフックなどを使いましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-219">
<a name="step_3_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 20というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4f/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1fd8a6ee9d9c40fc821b9344a40ed526" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/4f/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('1fd8a6ee9d9c40fc821b9344a40ed526')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 20というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/4f/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4f/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="1fd8a6ee9d9c40fc821b9344a40ed526"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/4\/4f\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/4\/4f\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-20.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">共用のタオルは横棒式のタオル掛けではなく、コート掛けフックにかける　</b>その方が場所も取らず、大きなタオルもしっかりとかけられます。また、コート掛けの方がタオルが早く乾きます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-220">
<a name="step_3_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 21というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/67/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="959dd7cd82c6adecb25f2d57e255cd41" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/67/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('959dd7cd82c6adecb25f2d57e255cd41')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 21というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/6/67/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/67/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="959dd7cd82c6adecb25f2d57e255cd41"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/6\/67\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/6\/67\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-21.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">キャビネットのドアの裏側に磁石のバーを張り付け、毛抜き、ヘアピン、化粧ブラシなどの磁石につく細かいものを収納する　</b>裏面がテープになった磁石を使うと壁を傷めません。収納したいものが磁石につくかどうか、事前に確認しましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-221">
<a name="step_3_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 22というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bc/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="6ddf55f37a53dd637944c0c24fb9e9c6" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/bc/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('6ddf55f37a53dd637944c0c24fb9e9c6')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 22というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/bc/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bc/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="6ddf55f37a53dd637944c0c24fb9e9c6"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/bc\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/bc\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-22.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">タブレットは大きな密封ポリ袋に入れると浴室でも安心して使える　</b>実際に浴室で試す前に、紙片を袋に入れて水に沈めてみます。紙が濡れたらその袋は完全防水ではないので、使用を避けましょう。ジップロックが最も良いでしょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-222">
<a name="step_3_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 23というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ce/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="37d298972e597ccccd89c75316b91f8e" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ce/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('37d298972e597ccccd89c75316b91f8e')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 23というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ce/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ce/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="37d298972e597ccccd89c75316b91f8e"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/ce\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/ce\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-23.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ハンドドリルにブラシを取り付け、いつもの洗剤を使って楽に磨き掃除をする　</b>この方法でどんな磨き掃除も楽にできます。ドリルに任せておけば、一生懸命ゴシゴシこする必要はありません。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-223">
<a name="step_3_6" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 24というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="16437b560d3ed4d17f220418a56ce35b" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('16437b560d3ed4d17f220418a56ce35b')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 24というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="16437b560d3ed4d17f220418a56ce35b"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/8\/8b\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/8\/8b\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-24.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">6</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">狭い寝室には、照明を天井から吊るす　</b>枕元にライトを置く場所が必要なくなり、部屋がより明るくなります。手作りにも挑戦してみましょう。
<ul>
<li>工作用ワイヤーを購入する　</li>
<li>ペンチでねじり、成形する</li>
<li>クリスマス用のライトを取り付ける　</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-224">
<a name="step_3_7" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 25というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="949291843edd5f91e523679e0ed2249e" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ca/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('949291843edd5f91e523679e0ed2249e')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 25というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/c/ca/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="949291843edd5f91e523679e0ed2249e"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/c\/ca\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/c\/ca\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-25.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">7</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">薄型の脱衣かごを手作りする　</b>ありふれた地味なものを買うより、刺繍用の丸い枠ときれいな色の布を使って手作りしてみましょう。袋を購入するか自分で縫い、袋の口を刺繍枠に被せて縫い付けます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-225">
<a name="step_3_8" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 26というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="54efa4719f2e038956353b9081708965" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('54efa4719f2e038956353b9081708965')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 26というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/e/e1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="54efa4719f2e038956353b9081708965"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/e\/e1\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/e\/e1\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-26.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">8</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">部屋の壁にペンキを塗る時は、ペンキにバニラエッセンスを大さじ1杯加える　</b>よく混ぜ合わせてから塗り始めます。500㏄程度塗るごとにさらに小さじ1杯のバニラエッセンスを入れ、混ぜ棒でよく混ぜます。こうすると、強いペンキの匂いが抑えられ、バニラのいい香りがするでしょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="wh_ad_inner w_label al_grey" data-service="adsense" data-slot="6771527778" data-width="728" data-height="90" data-smallheight="250" data-type="method" data-small="1" data-medium="1" data-channels="8866763126" data-mobilechannels="" data-largechannels="" data-smallchannels="" data-observerloading="1" data-sizes-array="0" data-gptdisplaylate="1"><div id="mobilemethod_ad_3"></div></div>
<script>WH.ads.addBodyAd('mobilemethod_ad_3')</script><div class="al_method">広告</div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
</ol>
<div class="clearall"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>4</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="ファッションのライフハック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E3.83.95.E3.82.A1.E3.83.83.E3.82.B7.E3.83.A7.E3.83.B3.E3.81.AE.E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 4 の 10:</div>ファッションのライフハック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_4" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-326">
<a name="step_4_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 27というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fcef608f520b682b1642d1d31c2ab1a7" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('fcef608f520b682b1642d1d31c2ab1a7')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 27というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f0/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="fcef608f520b682b1642d1d31c2ab1a7"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f0\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f0\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-27.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">TOMSなどの布製の靴を防水する　</b>潤滑用の蜜蝋ワックスを靴の表面に塗りつけます。外側をまんべんなく蜜蝋でカバーし、剥がれてきたら定期的に塗りなおします。ヘアドライヤーなどの熱でワックスの表面を溶かすと、目立ちにくくなります。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-327">
<a name="step_4_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 28というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/50/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="89a50b0e3d2baa63129d313394da7056" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/50/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('89a50b0e3d2baa63129d313394da7056')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 28というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/5/50/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/50/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="89a50b0e3d2baa63129d313394da7056"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/5\/50\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/5\/50\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-28.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<a href="/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%81%AA%E3%81%97%E3%81%A7%E6%B4%8B%E6%9C%8D%E3%81%AE%E3%82%B7%E3%83%AF%E3%82%92%E4%BC%B8%E3%81%B0%E3%81%99" title="アイロンなしで洋服のシワを伸ばす"><b class="whb">ストレートアイロンをアイロンとして使う</b></a><b class="whb">　</b>通常通りにアイロンを取り出し、温度が上がるのを待って使い、さらにすべてを片付けることを考えると、これはずっと簡単で効率的な方法です。彼女や姉妹、妻、娘などのストレートアイロンを借りるか、もしくは安価なものを近所のドラッグストアなどで購入しましょう。 
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-328">
<a name="step_4_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 29というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/ba/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dfe6906ec1ad4d385c8fb8055f3837d2" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/ba/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('dfe6906ec1ad4d385c8fb8055f3837d2')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 29というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/ba/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/ba/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="dfe6906ec1ad4d385c8fb8055f3837d2"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/ba\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/ba\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-29.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<a href="/%E8%B5%A4%E3%83%AF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%81%AE%E6%9F%93%E3%81%BF%E6%8A%9C%E3%81%8D%E3%82%92%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B" title="赤ワインの染み抜きをする"><b class="whb">赤ワインのシミ抜き</b></a><b class="whb">に白ワインを使う　</b>赤ワインのシミを抜くには、白ワインに浸した布でそっと叩きます。シミを広げないように、まずはボロ布で試してみましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-329">
<a name="step_4_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 30というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/96/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d142d3ff51970313ad06a410875cdc7f" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/96/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('d142d3ff51970313ad06a410875cdc7f')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 30というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/96/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/96/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d142d3ff51970313ad06a410875cdc7f"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/9\/96\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/9\/96\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-30.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">エナメル革の靴にはガラス用洗剤を使う　</b>ガラス用洗剤はエナメル革の靴の光沢を取り戻すのに使えます。汚れやシミのついた部分にスプレーし、きれいになるまで優しく拭き取ります。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-330">
<a name="step_4_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 31というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="14ff8e5d42893ecb01f073fd79a0707b" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/b8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('14ff8e5d42893ecb01f073fd79a0707b')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 31というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/b8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b8/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="14ff8e5d42893ecb01f073fd79a0707b"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/b8\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/b8\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-31.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">靴下がバラバラにならないように、洗濯機に入れる前に安全ピンでひとまとめにする　</b>こうすることで迷子になった靴下を探し回る必要がなくなります。安全ピンなど濡れても構わず、洗濯機で回しても外れないものを使用しましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
