<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>6</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="子育てのライフハック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.AD.90.E8.82.B2.E3.81.A6.E3.81.AE.E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 6 の 10:</div>子育てのライフハック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_6" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-540">
<a name="step_6_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 41というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/ad/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="87e265eac6add131da728ba5b599e068" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/ad/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('87e265eac6add131da728ba5b599e068')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 41というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/ad/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/ad/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="87e265eac6add131da728ba5b599e068"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/a\/ad\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/ad\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-41.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供がベビーベッドを卒業したら、机にリフォームする　</b>マットレスを外します。次に一方の側面を外し、次の子のために置いておくか、処分します。マットレスのサイズを測り、ちょうど同じ大きさの黒板を探します。必要に応じて、フックなどを取りつけましょう。 
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-541">
<a name="step_6_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 42というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/83/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="38896771feb20d65dfa293c708f308d9" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/83/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('38896771feb20d65dfa293c708f308d9')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 42というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/83/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/83/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="38896771feb20d65dfa293c708f308d9"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/8\/83\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/8\/83\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-42.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供が浴室などの鍵を中からかけられないようにする　</b>幅の広い輪ゴムをドアラッチの上で結びます。8の字型にし、内側と外側のドアノブにそれぞれの輪を通します。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-542">
<a name="step_6_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 43というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/ff/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="ce960cfbfbfff03e986bbd32040cfa0d" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/ff/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('ce960cfbfbfff03e986bbd32040cfa0d')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 43というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/ff/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/ff/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="ce960cfbfbfff03e986bbd32040cfa0d"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/ff\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/ff\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-43.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">トランポリンのばねで足を怪我しないように、プールヌードルでカバーをする　</b>プールヌードルを1/4に切り、片側に切れ目を入れます。切れ目は真っすぐでなくても構いませんが、その方がカバーしやすいでしょう。色鮮やかなプールヌードルがトランポリンの飾りにもなります。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-543">
<a name="step_6_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-44.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
