</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 45というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/dd/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/dd/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9663838360f36b10a070cb35cef3b5f0"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/d\/dd\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/d\/dd\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-45.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供用のテーブルをオイルクロスで覆い、防水ピクニックテーブルとして屋外で使う　</b>オイルクロスかビニール生地を購入し、ガムテープでテーブルに貼り付けます。単にガムテープで全体を覆うだけでも良いでしょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-545">
<a name="step_6_6" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-46.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
