<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/2\/2e\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-46.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-46.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/2\/2e\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-46.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-46.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">6</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">シーツとフラフープで秘密基地や仮設の更衣室を作る　</b>シーツを半分にたたんでフラフープの輪に通し、上から被せます。木に結び付け、上から吊るします。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-546">
<a name="step_6_7" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 47というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="ffa309141c7e44f6606f25fc87842661" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('ffa309141c7e44f6606f25fc87842661')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 47というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/f/f5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/f5/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="ffa309141c7e44f6606f25fc87842661"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/f\/f5\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/f\/f5\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-47.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">7</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">乳児に薬を飲ませる時に、あらかじめ切れ目を入れたおしゃぶりの中にスポイトを入れておく　</b>赤ちゃんはおしゃぶりに吸い付きますが、薬があるとは気付かないでしょう。再び同じおしゃぶりを持たせる際は、薬を完全に拭き取ってから渡しましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-547">
<a name="step_6_8" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 48というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/19/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d63376973c35ae4a957b688fc8481ef0" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/19/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('d63376973c35ae4a957b688fc8481ef0')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 48というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/19/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/19/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d63376973c35ae4a957b688fc8481ef0"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/1\/19\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/1\/19\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-48.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">8</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">シーツで赤ちゃん用ハンモックを作る　</b>シーツを斜めに置き、対角同士をテーブルの上で結びます。赤ちゃんの転落防止のために、残りの角は赤ちゃんの体を固定するように結びます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-548">
<a name="step_6_9" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 49というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/af/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="85142430e8aab34086b56e6d85ac83a0" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/af/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('85142430e8aab34086b56e6d85ac83a0')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 49というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/af/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/af/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="85142430e8aab34086b56e6d85ac83a0"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/a\/af\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/af\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-49.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">9</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供用に、親の電話番号の入ったブレスレットを作る　</b>子供を連れて公共の場に行く時は、必ずブレスレットを着用させます。迷子になったとしても、ブレスレットを見れば親への連絡先が分かります。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-549">
<a name="step_6_10" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 50というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/12/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="952145f05cf20ca2826964e00ebee685" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/12/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('952145f05cf20ca2826964e00ebee685')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 50というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/12/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/12/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="952145f05cf20ca2826964e00ebee685"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/1\/12\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/1\/12\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-50.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">10</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供がベッドから落ちる時は、プールヌードルで転落防止柵を作る　</b>ベッドの各辺にプールヌードルを置きます。上からシーツをかぶせ、ヌードルを固定します。ヌードルが堤防になり、ベッドの端まで来ても子供は落ちません。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-550">
<a name="step_6_11" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 51というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d9/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="136139745f0c86ba1609a34b8a1cfc4a" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d9/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('136139745f0c86ba1609a34b8a1cfc4a')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 51というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d9/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d9/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="136139745f0c86ba1609a34b8a1cfc4a"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/d\/d9\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/d\/d9\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-51.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">11</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">ビニールプールをベビーサークルとして使う　</b>底に毛布を敷き、おもちゃやクッションなどをたくさん入れます。底にも空気の入るプールなら、赤ちゃんが歩いても柔らかくて最適でしょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="wh_ad_inner w_label al_grey" data-service="adsense" data-slot="6771527778" data-width="728" data-height="90" data-smallheight="250" data-type="method" data-small="1" data-medium="1" data-channels="8866763126" data-mobilechannels="" data-largechannels="" data-smallchannels="" data-observerloading="1" data-sizes-array="0" data-gptdisplaylate="1"><div id="mobilemethod_ad_6"></div></div>
<script>WH.ads.addBodyAd('mobilemethod_ad_6')</script><div class="al_method">広告</div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
</ol>
<div class="clearall"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>7</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="学校生活のライフハック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E5.AD.A6.E6.A0.A1.E7.94.9F.E6.B4.BB.E3.81.AE.E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 7 の 10:</div>学校生活のライフハック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_7" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-651">
<a name="step_7_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 52というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bd/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="3b6a30e7dc64ef98dd09ef9516e4ac42" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/bd/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('3b6a30e7dc64ef98dd09ef9516e4ac42')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 52というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/b/bd/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bd/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="3b6a30e7dc64ef98dd09ef9516e4ac42"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/b\/bd\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/bd\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-52.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">学校でYouTubeなどのサイトがブロックされている場合は、<a href="/%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%82%B6%E3%81%AE%E3%83%97%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%99%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%83%A2%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89%E3%82%92%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%B9%E3%81%AB%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B" title="ブラウザのプライベートモードを有効にする"><b class="whb">クロームのプライベートモード</b></a>を使ってフィルターを回避する　</b>ただし、あまり頻繁に使いすぎると秘密がばれて二度と使えなくなってしまうため注意しましょう。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-652">
<a name="step_7_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 53というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9491415c554ed0c12a3f21cd61c3bfc0" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/00/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('9491415c554ed0c12a3f21cd61c3bfc0')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 53というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/0/00/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="9491415c554ed0c12a3f21cd61c3bfc0"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/0\/00\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/0\/00\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-53.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">テストでいい点を取るには、就寝前に<a href="/%E3%83%86%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E5%8B%89%E5%BC%B7%E3%82%92%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B" title="テスト勉強をする"><b class="whb">一番難しい部分を復習する</b></a>　</b>復習してすぐに眠ると、記憶が強化されます。ただし一夜漬けは避け、<a href="/%E5%8A%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%9A%84%E3%81%AB%E5%8B%89%E5%BC%B7%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B" title="効果的に勉強する">効率的に勉強しましょう</a>！
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-653">
<a name="step_7_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 54というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="6b4cc129b688cf860274e9c0d2fdeaa1" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('6b4cc129b688cf860274e9c0d2fdeaa1')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 54というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8b/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="6b4cc129b688cf860274e9c0d2fdeaa1"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/8\/8b\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/8\/8b\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-54.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">勉強中に噛んだものと同じ味のガムを噛むと、学習内容を思い出しやすくなる　</b>何かをはっきりと思い出すと（スイカ味のガムなど）、その時に勉強していたことも一緒に思い出します。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-654">
<a name="step_7_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 55というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/30/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d499365e3f44b3abb493a9b7e98c1b16" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/3/30/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('d499365e3f44b3abb493a9b7e98c1b16')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 55というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/3/30/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/30/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="d499365e3f44b3abb493a9b7e98c1b16"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/3\/30\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/3\/30\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-55.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">カード1枚の制限がある場合、要点メモを二重に書く　</b>まず赤インクで全体に書きます。それから、その上から青いインクで書きます。赤と青の３D眼鏡をかけ、自分が読みたい内容の色のレンズの方の目を閉じます。これならルール違反にはなりません。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-655">
<a name="step_7_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 56というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/13/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="206cc8c45e70330cd6aa57004304bbfe" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/13/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('206cc8c45e70330cd6aa57004304bbfe')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 56というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/1/13/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/1/13/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="206cc8c45e70330cd6aa57004304bbfe"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/1\/13\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/1\/13\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-56.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">千円札を定規として使う　</b>定規を忘れてしまっても、千円札があればそれを定規として使いましょう。千円札の長さは15㎝です。使用には注意を払い、おおよその測定にのみ使いましょう。 
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
