<div class="section steps   sticky">
<h3 class="in-block block_header">
<div class="altblock"><div>方法 <span>9</span>
</div>
</div>
<span id="買い物のライフハック"></span><span class="mw-headline" id=".E8.B2.B7.E3.81.84.E7.89.A9.E3.81.AE.E3.83.A9.E3.82.A4.E3.83.95.E3.83.8F.E3.83.83.E3.82.AF"><div class="method_label">方法 9 の 10:</div>買い物のライフハック</span>
</h3>
<div id="ステップ_9" class="section_text">
<ol class="steps_list_2">
<li id="step-id-862">
<a name="step_9_1" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 63というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="244e8a075aa07240a5ab9b450fe50324" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/a1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('244e8a075aa07240a5ab9b450fe50324')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 63というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/a/a1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a1/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="244e8a075aa07240a5ab9b450fe50324"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/a\/a1\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/a\/a1\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-63.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">1</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">アマゾンの返金制度を使う　</b>何かを購入してから30日以内に値段が下がった場合、差額分を返金してもらえます。カスタマーサービスのリンクからメールを送りましょう。　
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-863">
<a name="step_9_2" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 64というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="b9663b586599efe59bbd2057926faca7" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('b9663b586599efe59bbd2057926faca7')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 64というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/d/d7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d7/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="b9663b586599efe59bbd2057926faca7"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/d\/d7\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/d\/d7\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-64.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">2</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供の靴を買う際に本人を連れていかない場合、家を出る前に足型をとっておく　</b>線に沿って足型を切り抜きます。靴に入れてみて入るようなら、その靴は子供の足に合うと言えます。 
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-864">
<a name="step_9_3" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 65というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/48/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e5f80bbdf87b0834309d9a34f4d35b3a" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/48/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('e5f80bbdf87b0834309d9a34f4d35b3a')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 65というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/4/48/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/48/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="e5f80bbdf87b0834309d9a34f4d35b3a"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/4\/48\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/4\/48\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-65.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">3</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">Apple製品をオンラインで購入する時は、ショッピングカートに商品を入れ、チェックアウトはせずにそのまま7～10日ほど待つ　</b>そうすると、15～20％のディスカウントがもらえます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-865">
<a name="step_9_4" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 66というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/90/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="5eb369120b65d1bdda7acd1c88802e2d" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/90/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('5eb369120b65d1bdda7acd1c88802e2d')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 66というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/9/90/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/90/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="5eb369120b65d1bdda7acd1c88802e2d"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/9\/90\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/9\/90\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-66.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">4</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">飛行機のチケットをオンラインで購入する時は、<a href="/%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%82%B6%E3%81%AE%E3%82%AD%E3%83%A3%E3%83%83%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A5%E3%82%92%E3%82%AF%E3%83%AA%E3%82%A2%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B" title="ブラウザのキャッシュをクリアする"><b class="whb">ブラウザのキャッシュをクリアする</b></a>　</b>航空会社は購入者のサーチ結果を見て価格を上げてきます。これで5000円ほど節約できます。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-866">
<a name="step_9_5" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 67というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/73/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="82f6e9115bd4a891ac0fea942e86fa92" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/73/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('82f6e9115bd4a891ac0fea942e86fa92')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 67というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/7/73/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/73/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="82f6e9115bd4a891ac0fea942e86fa92"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/7\/73\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/7\/73\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-67.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">5</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">「マミーフック」（ベビーカー用クリップ）で買い物袋を一度に運ぶ　</b>実際には一度に運べる程度の荷物でも、スーパーのプラスチック袋が指に食い込んで運べないことがあります。マミーフックは、表面が柔らかく、握りやすくなっています。
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
<div class="scrolltomarker" data-isstep="1"></div>
</li>
<li id="step-id-867">
<a name="step_9_6" class="stepanchor"></a><div class="mwimg  largeimage  floatcenter " style="max-width:728px"><a href="#/%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB:Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg" class="image"><div class="content-spacer" style="padding-top:75%">
<img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 68というタイトルの画像" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="6d1fed335919d374b6cbd321770ba644" data-src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg"><script>WH.shared.addScrollLoadItem('6d1fed335919d374b6cbd321770ba644')</script>
</div>
<noscript><img alt="Use Life Hacks Step 68というタイトルの画像" src="https://www.wikihow.com/images_en/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg" decoding="async" class="whcdn content-fill" data-srclarge="https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/3a/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg" data-width="460" data-height="345" id="6d1fed335919d374b6cbd321770ba644"></noscript>
<div class="image_details" style="display:none;"><span style="display:none;">{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images_en\/thumb\/3\/3a\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg\/v4-460px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/3\/3a\/Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg\/v4-728px-Use-Life-Hacks-Step-68.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":728,"bigHeight":546,"licensing":"&lt;div class=\"mw-parser-output\"&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;"}</span></div></a></div>
<div class="step_num">6</div><div class="step">
<b class="whb">子供に高価なキャンバスを買わなくても、汚れていないピザの箱で代用する　</b>予備のピザ箱をくれるピザ店もあります。ドミノピザのような白く塗られた箱が一番使いやすいものの、何色の箱でも使えます。 
</div>
<div class="clearall"></div>
